<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ADEX FARM | Fresh Meat & Grocery Delivery Lagos</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Fresh meat, live cattle, goats, rams, and complete grocery supplies delivered to your doorstep in Lagos. Skip the market stress with Adex Farm.">
    
